{"tid":1659402,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張建宗稱電光火石間警察很難全部跟足規則做事","createTime":"2019-10-17T02:32:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T08:26:31.000Z","uid":56881,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"05ac8dffa106813e3eac3206ff6aca6d872b4028","tid":1659402,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:32:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97%E7%A8%B1%E9%9B%BB%E5%85%89%E7%81%AB%E7%9F%B3%E9%96%93%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%BE%88%E9%9B%A3%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E8%B7%9F%E8%B6%B3%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87%E5%81%9A%E4%BA%8B-015950554.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25AE%2597%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%2585%2589%25E7%2581%25AB%25E7%259F%25B3%25E9%2596%2593%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%25BE%2588%25E9%259B%25A3%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%2583%25A8%25E8%25B7%259F%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E8%25A6%258F%25E5%2589%2587%25E5%2581%259A%25E4%25BA%258B-015950554.html&d=o%2BN67aGUGKsADGfJqajrgIhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=e125fb9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97%E7%A8%B1%E9%9B%BB%E5%85%89%E7%81%AB%E7%9F%B3%E9%96%93%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%BE%88%E9%9B%A3%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E8%B7%9F%E8%B6%B3%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87%E5%81%9A%E4%BA%8B-015950554.html</a><br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗回應警察被指使用過分暴力時稱，在電光火石，好難要全部跟足規則做事，不會批評警方的行動部署，認為對警察有不滿，已有機制全面處理。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗出席商台節目時，回應施政報告未有談及警民關係的問題，他表示，施政報告主要是談及民生問題，警民關係不是著眼點，但不等如不重要，又說監警會已做了很多工作，年底亦會向特首提交首份報告。<br />\n<br />\n被問到有否準備要再上一層樓出任特首，張建宗表示，今日主題不是回應這個話題，強調問責團隊要有合作精神。再被追問如果有需要，是否願意接任，張建宗回應表示，假設問題現階段不回應，當務之急要讓香港走回正軌，再被問到是否在接任問題上不會「關後門」，他表示，不會評論這個問題，又讚揚特首林鄭月娥是相當能幹。<br />\n<br />\n又講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />陣間員佐級林大總統又發信不滿呀"},{"pid":"bc7dbe8ee2bf7b63863e6375a178ce45e46ea963","tid":1659402,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:33:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Yk6szE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Yk6szE.jpg&h=f0e63ff5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"eceec19561aa1e39f0d8e8d5bce426b8579a975e","tid":1659402,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:35:30.000Z","msg":"電光火石... bingo 又多個option"},{"pid":"cd82348fb2a893fc50905702b02e71a0b7fa2366","tid":1659402,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:36:26.000Z","msg":"張建宗不代表我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"305b90625e2596bb90eaeaf7ce02d2dec71891a5","tid":1659402,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:36:43.000Z","msg":"diu有錯就認la"},{"pid":"576d6bf36946019ece102427a3d798bc519c9fde","tid":1659402,"uid":137704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:36:44.000Z","msg":"即係承認唔跟規矩"},{"pid":"4869e6aaa7da93f76d0d7325c7244f72df10aaf4","tid":1659402,"uid":289259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:36:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"> IG &ldquo;bye bye starbucks&rdquo; challenge</span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1659200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1659200</a><br />\n<br />\n幫手推啦各位， 比美心負皮緊呀。"},{"pid":"e8ffb5e9acafc92db4ccb69ca7e9d33733cc091c","tid":1659402,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:36:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ee1bab59289ba15757dc8d11c25b64b0c214e90","tid":1659402,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:38:00.000Z","msg":"連登仔回應示威者被指使用過分暴力時稱，在電光火石，好難要全部跟足規則做事，不會批評示威者的行動部署，認為對示威者有不滿，已有機制全面處理，歡迎上連登開post討論。"},{"pid":"5e2cd19b05f56b8bf1eb24528542698e0163b798","tid":1659402,"uid":123053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB